<section class="differentiator-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Why 'Stack Solver'?</h2>
    <p class="philosophy">
      Because we don't believe in one-size-fits-all solutions. We analyse your challenges and
      objectives to build a <strong>'technology stack'</strong> – a customised combination
      of tools and strategies – that truly works for you.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .differentiator-section {
    background-color: #007bff; /* StackSolver Blue */
    color: #fff;
    padding: 3.5rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }
  .differentiator-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.3rem; /* British English might prefer rem or em, but sticking to original for now */
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .differentiator-section .philosophy {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
   .differentiator-section strong {
    font-weight: 600; /* Slightly more weight */
   }
</style>